snippet.title: Freakout: Calamity TV Show - HD Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Freshly released on Consoles (april, 17th 2020), you can catch the game on your favorite gaming platform !

Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/freakout-calamity-tv-show-switch/

Playstation4: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP3252-CUSA18427_00-JANDUSOFT0000001

Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/freakout-calamity-tv-show/9mtzkv7tpbh0?activetab=pivot:overviewtab

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/848430/Freakout__Calamity_TV_Show/

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Freakout : Calamity TV Show is a juicy Top-Down-Dual-Stick-Shooter inspired by old school arcade games and more recent Die & Retry shooters.
In a disturbed dystopia filled with mutants and killing machines, you’re the star of a reality show [...]

Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/Freakout-Calamity-TV-Show-1766440456745319
Web : http://freakout-calamity-tv-show.com/
